{"tid":1404177,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］港安醫院個人資料收集聲明有改動","createTime":"2019-08-04T03:09:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T14:20:47.000Z","uid":267113,"like":96,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6409e560bbe07c27d9b28d564cbe3a82d4186952","tid":1404177,"uid":267113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:09:56.000Z","msg":"我朋友既朋友既朋友係港安啲舊病人，今日去港安睇醫生，個啲感冒傷風咁。跟手就要簽份個人資料聲明咁，你知間間都要簽個啲呢。佢就覺得咁古怪，之前咪簽過囉，咁然後簽完發現有一句「授權醫院.....香港特別行政區政府單位作......法規遵從......的用途」。咁無啦啦做乜之前簽完又簽呢？咁醫院話因為第五條係有改動過咁喎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E12RDN9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE12RDN9.jpg&h=8908e289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坦白講政府收集數據作政策規劃就好正常既，不過，因為私隱條例咁講既：<br />\n<br />\n私隱條例訂明的六項保障資料原則<br />\n任何人士或機構在收集、持有、處理或使用個人資料時，必須遵守條例第4條及附表1訂明的六項保障資料原則。(註: 被收集個人資料的當事人稱為「資料當事人」，而收集他人的個人資料的人士或機構則稱為「資料使用者」。)<br />\n第一項原則 ─ 收集個人資料的目的及方式<br />\n個人資料必需要為合法目的而收集，收集目的亦須直接與使用該等資料的資料使用者之職能或活動有關。所收集到的資料足夠便可，而<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不應超過有關目的之實際需要</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n咁即係話，唔係實際需要既要求，你<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">可以拒絕</span></span>架喎。問題係，醫院係唔會主動同你講既，咁你記住自己同佢講，做個醒目保護私隱既香港人喇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dkHBPYc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdkHBPYc.jpg&h=a83f660a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">仲有，唔一定港安先有，其他醫院都可能有，大家小心保護私隱啦。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc7fe0416b79a388c1ec700cc6bbebbb782dffc","tid":1404177,"uid":267113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:19:25.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"3eec1e555e65b6a6220d33b0a59cb3df93f9b110","tid":1404177,"uid":267113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:19:52.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"68933b074f4dcb4f44d3a53e5ba52ed67aa07b60","tid":1404177,"uid":127168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:20:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a077c1f3ab456be8550ccdc211fd00c67b05d79","tid":1404177,"uid":164845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:20:30.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"713142c1c1b7406e91a31df549265b4923efdf67","tid":1404177,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dea92610e1cc48a5b1a727f9bfb942ba6ef0b5e","tid":1404177,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:20:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"474328c3c0397aa33756e7eca2da9c2ac3e6052a","tid":1404177,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:20:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b643e3359c66e1b6b9b2181650faa32ff560de","tid":1404177,"uid":214672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:21:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a34e12eb4da1f1eb6e25eaac5da77f7929b46a00","tid":1404177,"uid":267113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:22:58.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"5726806ac2b1c84548fe97ac434f069ac15f3873","tid":1404177,"uid":267113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-0